com.google.cloud.compute.deprecated

Class SchedulingOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.compute.deprecated.SchedulingOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class SchedulingOptions
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A Google Compute Engine instance scheduling options. When there are system events that might cause your instances to be disrupted, Google Compute Engine automatically manages the scheduling decisions for your instances. Use SchedulingOptions.preemptible() to create a preemptible instance. Use SchedulingOptions.standard() to configure scheduling options for a standard instance.
    See Also:
    Setting Instance Scheduling Options, Serialized Form
